e i \u00e5r.", "Som f\u00f8lge av konkursen m\u00e5tte ogs\u00e5 Cafe Dr. Livingstone innstille driften. Administrerende direkt\u00f8r Bj\u00f8rn Ole Myhr i Realinvest satser p\u00e5 en gjen\u00e5pning s\u00e5 snart aktuelle leietakere kommer p\u00e5 plass."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|trondheim"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "48cf6405f67f9ce4c0428f1891b1558747503f0d620229968fb99e5eadd23079"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-05-02T06:02:27.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Langtidsleie fremfor tradisjonell hotelldrift skal sikre fremtiden for det konkursrammede sentrumshotellet Fru Sch\u00f8ller."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1095599.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/ver2%20hotell01"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/7b758d3bebb8b522a067867bf344a125344f603b.jpg?597ca8f7"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": "Ny start for Fru Sch\u00f8ller -adressa.no"}, {"field": "id", "value": "7b758d3bebb8b522a067867bf344a125344f603b"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "trondheim"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "travel"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["driften", "hotell", "dag"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["prinsens", "fru sch\u00f8ller apartment", "dronningen bed", "realinvest", "cafe dr", "hotell fru sch\u00f8ller", "linn\u00e9a", "stiftsg\u00e5rdsparken", "dronningens", "fru sch\u00f8ller", "breakfast", "\u00f8yvind og henrik carstens hotel fru sch\u00f8ller", "comfort hotel park"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, 